doc.title: ratonga o waho
doc.description: Ka paato koe i tetahi hono, ka taea e koe te whakamohio atu ki te ratonga o waho kua pawhiria tetahi hono Ka taea e koe te whakamahi i tenei mahi mena ka hiahia koe ki te huri i te tirotiro tirotiro.

service.title: Kei te hiahia koe ki tetahi ratonga o waho hei whakatinana i tenei mahi, ka whakaratohia e matou he putanga beta o te ratonga
service.linkExplain: Ka taea e koe te tango i te tono e rite ana ki te punaha whakahaere e whakamahia ana e koe. Karekau i te whakapumau ka taea te whakahaere i raro i nga punaha katoa Mena ka raru koe, mena ka mohio koe ki te {{0}} reo papatono, ka taea e koe te tango i te waehere puna me te whakahiato.

sendParams.title: Ina pawhiria te orite, ka tukuna he ahanoa ki waho ma te whakamahi i te {{0}}, kei roto nga huanga e whai ake nei:
sendParams.page: Ko te wahitau o te wharangi o naianei
